Q - two types of export/import
Default  export/import
export default Component;
Import Component from “path”

Named export/import
export const Component
Import {Component} form “path”


#React Hooks
(Normal JS Utility Function)
- useState() - superpowerful state Variables
- useEffect()

Whenever a state variable update, react re-render the components.

Reconciliation Algorithm (React fiber - react16)
virtual DOM(javaScript object representation) is the representation of actual DOM
Read the Document : acdite link (https://github.com/acdlite/react-fiber-architecture)

Why React is fast?
Ans - Efficient DOM manipulation

