Lecture : 6
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-> Monolothic VS Microservices
-> Seperation of Convern

Approach 1
App Loads --> API (wait for data tooks 500ms) --> Render (more lagging)

Approach 2
Loads --> Render(website skeleton) --> API (geys data tooks 500ms) --> Re-render (data with less Lagging)


-> useEffect Hooks
---------------------
When the body function will render, useEffect will render it, as soon as it complete render it will call the callback function


